### Attribution for LLM-Generated Content

Some example files and taxonomy entries contain content that was generated with
the assistance of a large language model (LLM). These files carry attribution
metadata in their frontmatter, specifically the `llm_model` and
`llm_prompt_file` fields. Human review and editorial judgment was applied to
all LLM-assisted content before inclusion in this repository.

